name: プロデューサー
text: ──卵焼きは、甘い派か？　しょっぱい派か？
trans: ──When it comes to tamagoyaki, are you the sweet camp? Savory camp?

name: プロデューサー
text:
いや、すまん……
さっき出先で、そういう話になって──
trans:
Uh, no, sorry...
Just, on the way here, that came up, and──

name: 透
text:
え？　うん
──あ、心配してくれたんだ
trans:
Huh? Yeah.
──Ah, you were worried about me.

name: 透
text:
え？　ううん……
ていうか
trans:
Eh? No, I am...
Though, actually.

name: 透
text:
え、ううん……
考えてたけど
trans:
Eh? Not really...
I was just thinking about it.

name: 透
text:
作ってくれるとか
そういう話じゃなくて？
trans:
It sounded like you were going to make some,
or something. Was that not it?

name: プロデューサー
text: （うっ……しまった。別のことを言えば良かったな……）
trans: (Ah... I should've said something else instead...)
